    <item>
      <title>纽约市移民危机不会从霍楚尔获得新资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/new-york-city-s-migrant-crisis-to-get-no-new-funding-from-hochul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州长凯西·霍楚尔 (Kathy Hochul) 不会向纽约市提供任何新资金来帮助其应对移民危机，这是一个重大转变，因为数以万计的寻求庇护者使该市的预算捉襟见肘，需要政府的帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/new-york-city-s-migrant-crisis-to-get-no-new-funding-from-hochul</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 18:08:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
